                                    should not exceed 180 per 100 mL, calculated as the geometric
                                    mean of all samples collected from March to October inclusive in
                                    one calendar year. Samples should be taken at least 3 times in a
                                    calendar month at intervals of between 3 and 14 days.</content></paragraph>
