            river catchment boundary in the south west, and by a line between a point south of Tseng
            Tau San Tsuen
                (22º16<i>&apos;</i>19<i>&quot;</i>N,
                113º59<i>&apos;</i>04<i>&quot;</i>E)
            and Tsoi Yuen Tsuen
                (22º16<i>&apos;</i>12<i>&quot;</i>N,
                113º59<i>&apos;</i>13<i>&quot;</i>E)
